---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
README to Translate from HIN-ENG or ENG-HIN using Selenium Web Driver for Firefox
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Important Note : Please check the usage policy of https://www.bing.com/translator before using it.


================================
Install the selenium web driver:
-> pip install selenium

Install the pyperclip module:
-> pip install pyperclip
================================

================================================================================================
Download the latest version of geckodriver from: https://github.com/mozilla/geckodriver/releases
Extract and paste the driver in the '/usr/bin' or '/usr/local/bin' directory.
================================================================================================

===========================================================
Two scripts are there in the folder:
1. 'bing_eng_hin.py' converts data in English to Hindi.
2. 'bing_hin_eng.py' converts text in Hindi to English.
===========================================================

==============================================================
Command:
-> python script_name.py <input_file> <output_file>

Replace script_name.py with the name of the script given above.
===============================================================